{
  "name": "Finance Vector Refresh",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 17 3 * * *"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "cron",
      "name": "Daily 03:17 UTC",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [240, 240]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "manual",
      "name": "Manual Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.manualTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, 420]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "http://finance-vector:8095/refresh",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "Authorization",
              "value": "=Bearer {{$env.FINANCE_VECTOR_TOKEN}}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendQuery": true,
        "queryParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "recreate",
              "value": "false"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {
          "timeout": 15000,
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "neverError": true,
              "responseFormat": "json"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "refresh",
      "name": "POST /refresh",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [560, 320]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "amount": 30,
        "unit": "seconds"
      },
      "id": "wait",
      "name": "Wait 30s",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.wait",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [780, 320]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "http://finance-vector:8095/status",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 10000,
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "neverError": true,
              "responseFormat": "json"
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "status",
      "name": "GET /status",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1000, 320]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Finance Vector Refresh\n\nDaily refresh of the `finance_assets` Qdrant collection (top 250 stocks + top 250 crypto).\n\n**Trigger paths**\n- Schedule: 03:17 UTC daily (matches the in-process scheduler — disable one of them if you want a single source of truth)\n- Manual: click *Execute Workflow*\n\n**Auth**\nThe seeder requires `Authorization: Bearer $FINANCE_VECTOR_TOKEN` if that env var is set on the dream-finance-vector container. Make sure n8n was started with the same `FINANCE_VECTOR_TOKEN` (already wired in `extensions/services/n8n/compose.yaml` once you add it).\n\n**What it does**\n1. POST /refresh — fire-and-forget, returns 202 immediately\n2. Wait 30s\n3. GET /status — pull last_summary / last_error so the workflow log shows the result",
        "height": 320,
        "width": 460
      },
      "id": "note",
      "name": "Notes",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, -100]
    }
  ],
  "connections": {
    "Daily 03:17 UTC": {
      "main": [[{"node": "POST /refresh", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    },
    "Manual Trigger": {
      "main": [[{"node": "POST /refresh", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    },
    "POST /refresh": {
      "main": [[{"node": "Wait 30s", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    },
    "Wait 30s": {
      "main": [[{"node": "GET /status", "type": "main", "index": 0}]]
    }
  },
  "settings": {
    "executionOrder": "v1"
  },
  "meta": {
    "templateId": "finance-vector-refresh"
  },
  "tags": [{"name": "finance"}]
}

